[[span style="font-family: Baskerville Old Face;"]] [[size 350%]]Ori's Art Page[[/size]] [[/span]]

Welcome one and all! My name is Ori, you may have heard of me before! While I am a writer and have done a ton of literary work for the site, I've also been a digital artist for quite a while. I don't consider myself amazing or a professional by any means, but I'm pretty proud of my work. I don't have many SCP focused pieces yet, but a collection of what I do have is below!

